title: Guess who Tahm Kench devoured?
body:
Just finished this today! Was excited about the idea so started non-stop drawing immediately :D
Guess who's in Tahm Kench's mouth? {{champion:223}}

This is really well done :)  Reminds me of "Who's That Pokemon" but far more morbid!  I got all but Singed when I tried it myself (which I should know, as my artist friend pretty much plays Singed exclusively - the cackling laughter as people chase him is epic.)
Does singed's poison trail work while he's devoured? I know swain's ult does, but this could be a thing

IT'S PIKACHU! 

Seriously, though, these are super awesome. :3
Thanks! I think the ability itself is already far more morbid :P {{champion:223}}
